~       if condition
byte    uint8_t
countof sizeof(array) / sizeof(array[0])
eod     end of data
exit    return
hand    handler
le      little endian
ptr     pointer
uint    uint32_t
undef   undefined
word    uint16_t

EP      endpoint
HW      hardware
ISR     interrupt service routine
MAC     media access control
NPU     network processor unit
PHY     physical layer
RTOS    real time OS
RX      host → device (EP-OUT)
TX      device → host (EP-IN)
SME     state machine engine
